ckquote><blockquote>唔洗你講，我講咗先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Who Fucking Cares?</span><br />\n<br />\n我發現習慣咗連登個模式係件好恐怖嘅事<br />\n當初逃離高登，以為連狗係好人，以為終於揾到個烏托邦<br />\n<br />\n上咗呢一年幾，開始發現<br />\n無晒改圖<br />\n無晒改詞<br />\n潮文無人睇得明<br />\n講豬柳強都會畀人笑<br />\n除咗雞之外就無第二句<br />\n唔明黃子華都會有人大大聲講出嚟<br />\n<br />\n連登上至個名，下至icon，有咩唔係來自高登<br />\n好嘅就繼承唔到，膠嘅就學到應一應<br />\n<br />\n林狗連狗都唔係咩好人，我未必會上返高登<br />\n但至少我已經唔想再做連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n循例貼下BAM圖，如果連狗唔BAM我就自己亂改密碼同email</blockquote>走就走啦<br />\n貼呢d唔會bam架好似高登咁無自由咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>連狗幫你轉返做link<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>貼j圖會bam<br />\n己經証明高登垃圾</blockquote><br />\nJ圖 BAM圖都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁貼J圖高登點會BAM呀 傻撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔識分就唔識分啦 新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c818583d4ecda997b458450546bda94db337612d","tid":610702,"uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"連匪就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長毛賊肯定唔荒好人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你見連登咁多5毛就知啦<br />\n<br />\n所以我一直都話<br />\n連登=匪國<br />\n高登先=中華民國<br />\n呼籲大家一齊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回家</span></span>,牙joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}